obile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532508\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tsv1665702747305.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tsv1665702747305.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tsv1665702747305.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tsv1665702747305\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Network Cloud-Served License </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__cloud_served_network_license_203136\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__p_d67118e1_d67119e1_d67120e1\">A network cloud-served license enables a Sentinel RMS\n         License Manager (also called an RMS Server) to run concurrent licenses from a network\n         location, synchronizing with the Sentinel Cloud Server to automatically extend and renew\n         licenses.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__p_d67121e1_d67122e1_d67123e1\">You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with Uniface. It enables you to activate and configure cloud-served licenses for the RMS Sentinel License Manager.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__p_d67124e1_d67125e1_d67126e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"paz1665702747377.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/paz1665702747377.html\">Sentinel RMS License Manager</a>.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__li_d29780e1_d29781e1_d29782e1\">To configure a network cloud-served license, see\n               <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"izl1665702748868.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/izl1665702748868.html\" title=\"A network cloud-served license enables a Sentinel RMS License Manager to run concurrent licenses from a network location\">Configuring Network Cloud-Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tsv1665702747305__li_d29783e1_d29784e1_d29785e1\">To return a network cloud-served license, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cwt1665702749016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwt1665702749016.html\">Returning Network Cloud-Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/paz1665702747377.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sentinel RMS License Manager</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cjh1665702747666.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Installing the Sentinel RMS License Manager on Windows</a><p>The Sentinel Rights Management System (RMS) License Manager enforces and manages licenses for Uniface in multi-user environments.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dhe1665702749084.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uninstalling Sentinel RMS License Manager on Windows</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fnb1665702748208.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Installing the Sentinel RMS License Manager on Unix and Linux</a><p>The Sentinel Rights Management System (RMS) License Manager (also known as the RMS Server) enforces and manages licenses for Uniface in multi-user environments.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luh1665702748423.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uninstalling Sentinel RMS License Manager on Unix</a><p>To uninstall the RMS License Manager, use the uninstall script that was created in the directory you specified during installation. You will be asked to return your license so that you can use it on a different machine.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532508\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532508\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Network Cloud-Served License Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Network Cloud-Served License A network cloud-served license enables a Sentinel RMS License Manager (also called an RMS Server) to run concurrent licenses from a network location, synchronizing with the Sentinel Cloud Server to automatically extend and renew licenses. You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with Uniface. It enables you to activate and configure cloud-served licenses for the RMS Sentinel License Manager. For more information, see Sentinel RMS License Manager . To configure a network cloud-served license, see Configuring Network Cloud-Served Licenses . To return a network cloud-served license, see Returning Network Cloud-Served Licenses . Related Links Sentinel RMS License Manager Installing the Sentinel RMS License Manager on Windows The Sentinel Rights Management System (RMS) License Manager enforces and manages licenses for Uniface in multi-user environments. Uninstalling Sentinel RMS License Manager on Windows Installing the Sentinel RMS License Manager on Unix and Linux The Sentinel Rights Management System (RMS) License Manager (also known as the RMS Server) enforces and manages licenses for Uniface in multi-user environments. Uninstalling Sentinel RMS License Manager on Unix To uninstall the RMS License Manager, use the uninstall script that was created in the directory you specified during installation. You will be asked to return your license so that you can use it on a different machine. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}